## 🚀 Starting a New Analysis

1. Copy all 4 templates into `analyses/TICKER/`
2. Give Claude the ticker — he'll research what he can and flag yellow cells needing sourced data
3. Fill `Assumptions` tab first → `Financials` → `Valuation` + `Technical`
4. Complete `analysis.md` sections 1–8
5. Update `DATA` block in `chart.html` with price levels

