## 📋 Write-Up Sections

| # | Section | Key Content |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Business & Moat | What they do, competitive advantages |
| 2 | Financial Snapshot | Revenue, margins, FCF, ROIC |
| 3 | Valuation | DCF (Bear/Base/Bull), CAGR, comps vs. industry |
| 4 | Technical Analysis | S/R levels, MAs, price action, reversal signals |
| 5 | Catalysts | Near / medium / long-term |
| 6 | Risks | Risk matrix + thesis-breakers |
