## 🎯 BUY Criteria

- [ ] Below DCF fair value or at discount to industry P/E
- [ ] Quality business: durable moat, positive FCF, manageable debt
- [ ] Meaningful drawdown — entry at value, not euphoria
- [ ] At or near key technical support (200-day, prior low, gap fill)
- [ ] Reversal signal: higher low, SMA reclaim, volume confirmation
- [ ] R/R: target upside ≥ 2x downside to stop

